description:
An amazing, special vintage item. This Gucci handbag is very rare and we are so, so happy to have it in our store. Bought during 1950‘s from a very elegant lady (at that time, now she is a beloved grandma!) from Milan. 

Note: Early Vintage Gucci handbags (from the 1950's -1970's) do not feature a serial number. Historicaly searched and confirmed all handbags produced by Gucci during the 1950‘s-70‘s feature a Gold Gucci Stamp instead of a Tag. The earlier versions have "made in Italy by Gucci" or just the Gold Gucci Shield embedded on the inside or the strap.

This handbag is in a very good condition (little signs of wear and no tears at all).
